reviewText: First of all, I've been to some Luke shows back in the early 90's, when you actually knew that he was going to bring the baddest, nastiest freaks with him. Sadly this is no longet the case. I've got Spring Break footage tighter than this, with thighter chicks doing freakier things.  Maybe if I was 14 then I would be all over this.  Leave this one alone....
This was a massive disapointment, too much talking from luke and his boyz and not enough of the girls. Dont waste your money!!

Again, Luke really delivers.  If you are a fan of any of Luke's previous work, you'll love this.  Luther Campbell delivers a plethora of women doing the wildest of things.  This video is the ultimate for anybody that loves to see beautiful women getting wild and crazy.  A must have for all Luke's Freakshow and Peep Show fans.
